#, no-wrap
msgid "A Tale of 2 Coal-Fired Power Stations"
msgstr "Historia de dos centrales térmicas de carbón"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:119
msgid "31 MAY & 4 JUNE | Germany & Czech Republic"
msgstr "31 de mayo y 4 de junio | Alemania y República Checa"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:121
msgid ""
"While Czech rebels were celebrating the shutdown of one of Europe’s dirtiest "
"coal-fired power stations, rebels across Europe were protesting the launch "
"of a brand-new one in Germany."
msgstr ""
"Mientras los rebeldes checos celebraban el cierre de una de las centrales "
"térmicas de carbón más contaminantes, los rebeldes de toda Europa "
"protestaban contra la inauguración de una nueva en Alemania."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:123
msgid ""
"![Rebel with an extinction rebellion flag in front of power station](/assets/"
"uploads/NEWSLETTERIMAGE7.jpg)"
msgstr ""
"![Rebel with an extinction rebellion flag in front of power station](/assets/"
"uploads/NEWSLETTERIMAGE7.jpg)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:125
msgid ""
"On 4th June the state-owned Prunerov 1 power station near the town of Kadan, "
"north-west of Prague, was finally closed down. According to a 2007 study by "
"the World Wildlife Fund, Prunéřov was Europe’s 12th worst power station in "
"terms of its energy efficiency and CO2 output.[](https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Carbon_dioxide)"
msgstr ""
"El 4 de junio, la central térmica estatal Prunerov 1 cerca de la ciudad de "
"Kadan, al noroeste de Praga, se cerró definitivamente. De acuerdo con un "
"estudio de 2007 realizado por el World Wildlife Fund, Prunéřov ocupaba el "
"puesto número 12 en la lista de las peores centrales eléctricas de Europa en "
"términos de eficiencia energética y emisiones de CO2.[](https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Carbon_dioxide)"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:127
msgid ""
"Four days earlier the controversial [Datteln4](https://twitter.com/hashtag/"
"StopDatteIn4?src=hashtag_click) power station near Dortmund had been started "
"up, with its operator Uniper claiming it to be among the world’s most modern "
"and efficient coal-fired power plants."
msgstr ""
"Cuatro días antes, la polémica [Datteln4](https://twitter.com/hashtag/"
"StopDatteIn4?src=hashtag_click) cercana a Dortmund entraba en "
"funcionamiento, mientras su operador Uniper afirmaba que esta central "
"térmica de carbón es una de las más modernas y eficientes mundo."

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-06-17-newsletter-40.md:129
msgid ""
"But as [protestors](https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=2Cs1DKyshAw&feature=youtu.be) made clear, it is still burning coal and "
"still adding to the burden of CO2 in the Earth’s atmosphere. Greta Thunberg "
"called it “a shameful day for Europe”."
msgstr ""
"Pero [los manifestantes](https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=2Cs1DKyshAw&feature=youtu.be) dejaron bien claro que sigue quemando carbón "
"y emitiendo CO2 a la atmósfera terrestre. Greta Thunberg declaró que se "
"trata de “un día vergonzoso para Europa”."

